Forging Connections between Supply and Manufacturing

About

Frank Longo, with a background as a progressive deep draw toolmaker and head of sales, is the owner of FCL Consulting and Sales. Specializing in progressive metal stamping, CNC machining, sheet metal fabrication, and metal finishing, Frank leverages his extensive experience to forge robust connections between supply chains and top-tier manufacturers. His expertise extends to assisting in engineering for New Product Introduction (NPI) and optimizing manufacturability for mass production.

Company

FCL Consulting and Sales is dedicated to constructing enduring partnerships between supply chains and industry-leading manufacturers. As a company, FCL excels in progressive metal stamping, CNC machining, sheet metal fabrication, and metal finishing. With a foundation built on Frank's background as a toolmaker and head of sales, coupled with his co-ownership of a third-generation manufacturing company, FCL brings a unique and seasoned perspective to drive success for both the company and its clients.
